[OVERLAY] VimFu — Send Literal Prefix
[SAY] Control B is the tmux prefix. But what if a program inside tmux also uses control B? Like the Bash readline shortcut to move the cursor back?
[SAY] Type some text. Now control B, control B sends a literal control B to the shell. The cursor moves back one character.
